text: The 1993 Big Eight Men's Basketball Tournament was held March 12–14 at Kemper Arena in Kansas City, Missouri. Seventh-seeded defeated #5 seed in the championship game, 68–56, to earn the conference's automatic bid to the 1993 NCAA Tournament. ==Bracket== ==References== Tournament Category:Big Eight Conference Men's Basketball Tournament Big Eight Conference Men's Basketball Tournament
